package com.tencent.wstt.gt.manager;

import com.tencent.wstt.gt.InPara;
import com.tencent.wstt.gt.OutPara;

/**
 * 目前，唯一的AUT客户端并没有初始的出参和入参
 */
<fim_suffix>public class AUTClient extends Client {

	public AUTClient() {
		super(ClientManager.AUT_CLIENT);
	}

	@Override
	public IInParaManager initInParas(InPara[] inParas) {
		IInParaManager im = new DefaultInParaManager(this);
		if (null != inParas)
		{
			for (InPara ip : inParas)
			{
				im.register(ip);
			}
		}

		return im;
	}

	@Override
	public IOutParaManager initOutParas(OutPara[] outParas) {
		IOutParaManager om = new ConnectedOutParaManager(this);
		if (null != outParas)
		{
			for (OutPara op : outParas)
			{
				om.register(op);
			}
		}

		return om;
	}

}<fim_middle>// class below has no smell
